  "detailed_description": "The game of bowls is a very old sport, which requires skill, strategy and a little luck.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1099010/extras/04b469c15b5ca19ec142769f0bfa4501.avif?t=1560952109\" width=400 height=84 /></span><br>Bocce VR allows you to experience the excitement of a large game of bowling, challenging the computer.<br>Play inside the stadium of a real bocce club, the atmosphere and tension will be skyrocketing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1099010/extras/f33ba65cb6251bbac91e5f3b7a658a49.avif?t=1560952109\" width=400 height=84 /></span><br>Show that you master this sport with cunning and skill, decide which strategies you use in the game to defeat your opponent.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple and good look<br></li><li>Realistic and interacting audience<br></li><li>Good and funny music</li></ul>",
